♪Grind flesh between grit and stone♪

232
00:13:05,901 --> 00:13:10,221
♪Sink into pain,
only then are pearls born♪

233
00:13:13,613 --> 00:13:17,517
♪Wait until abyssal darkness
stains every inch of skin♪

234
00:13:19,661 --> 00:13:24,717
♪Then comes the time to chase the dawn♪

235
00:13:27,309 --> 00:13:31,917
♪I'll sweep through dusty sands♪

236
00:13:32,525 --> 00:13:35,501
♪Passing wind♪

237
00:13:35,917 --> 00:13:39,117
♪Entwine my hair in dance♪

238
00:13:41,069 --> 00:13:45,549
♪I'll lean into his embrace♪

239
00:13:46,157 --> 00:13:49,197
♪Wade through deep seas♪

240
